2
00:01:22,340 --> 00:01:27,780
=My Marvellous Fable=

3
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:40,020
=Episode 20=

4
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:50,820
I'll light it first.

5
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:53,460
Do you even know how to do it?

6
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:54,700
Not really.

7
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,580
You never played this before?

8
00:01:58,340 --> 00:01:59,580
Will it burn my hand?

9
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,460
You scared me.

10
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:10,300
You're actually afraid of sparklers?

11
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:12,700
This is how you play it.

12
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,300
Are we conducting an orchestra here?

13
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:29,820
How is the team?

14
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:32,780
I don't know.

15
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:33,980
I didn't pay attention to them.

16
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,540
Didn't you go to work?

17
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:38,260
I did.

18
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:40,700
However,

19
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,340
the only thing on my mind was...

20
00:02:44,620 --> 00:02:45,540
Was it me?

21
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:49,340
I... I was trying to find you.

22
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:51,580
I see.

23
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:56,020
I met Luna too.

24
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:57,060
Oh.

25
00:02:58,820 --> 00:02:59,420
Oh?

26
00:03:03,340 --> 00:03:04,020
Oh?

27
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:06,500
Do you think that explains everything?

28
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:08,740
Yeah.

29
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:10,180
Oh means oh.

30
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:11,540
It doesn't have any meaning to it.

31
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:22,740
Don't do this again.

32
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,900
I was just worried about you.

33
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:29,980
You were worried about me?

34
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,020
If you were worried about me,

35
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:34,020
you wouldn't have left
without saying a word.

36
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,340
You're not a criminal.

37
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,780
How could you

38
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:38,860
vanish

39
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,220
without saying a word?

40
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:42,260
I didn't vanish.

41
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:44,100
You said nothing,

42
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,820
and you became unreachable.
That's called vanishing.

43
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:49,780
You're getting ahead of yourself, huh?

44
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:53,500
You'd do the same if you went through

45
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,500
what I went through.

46
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,180
I was worried about you

47
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:57,340
and your novel.

48
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:57,940
The team

49
00:03:57,940 --> 00:03:59,500
was acting suspiciously too.

50
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:03,020
That's because you kept urging me
for the manuscripts all day long.

51
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:04,260
Is there nothing else between us

52
