besides the manuscripts?

53
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,580
Didn't I tell you already?

54
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:12,060
The manuscripts don't matter.

55
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:18,380
The manuscripts don't matter?

56
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:23,340
Are you sure they don't?

57
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:30,260
I'm finally free!

58
