a different meaning to me.

60
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,780
What's the difference?

61
00:04:47,020 --> 00:04:48,260
In the past, urging you

62
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,700
for the manuscripts was my task.

63
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:54,060
Sometimes, I get stressed out.

64
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:58,620
What about now?

65
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:03,820
At least I can spend time with you

66
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,460
when I urge you for the manuscripts now.

67
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:12,060
Looks like you've recovered
from your illness.

68
00:05:13,020 --> 00:05:13,700
Illness?

69
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:15,420
It's nothing.

70
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:22,780
Tell me.

71
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:23,740
What illness did you mean?

72
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,260
Feng Tianlan,

73
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:39,620
