77
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,220
I have.

78
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:37,180
How is she doing then?

79
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:41,220
She...

80
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,020
She's doing well.

81
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:45,340
Good job,

82
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:45,780
Feng.

83
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:48,060
You two should catch
the last flight for today.

84
00:06:48,060 --> 00:06:49,580
I'll tell Ziyun to pick you guys up.

85
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:51,060
It's pretty late now.

86
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,420
We'll return tomorrow.

87
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:54,420
Sir,

88
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:55,340
don't worry.

89
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:56,340
This is my personal affair.

90
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:57,420
I won't ask for reimbursements.

91
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:58,500
Alright then.

92
00:06:59,100 --> 00:06:59,780
Okay.

93
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:00,340
If so, Feng,

94
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:01,300
ask her

95
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:03,540
if she could give me
a complete version of the sample book.

96
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:04,500
Sample book?

97
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,580
I'm not sure about that.

98
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:07,820
Let me ask her for you.

99
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,940
I'm getting annoyed here.

100
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:12,260
Got it.

101
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:13,820
He hung up.

102
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:57,620
Actually, I've been thinking of this

103
00:07:58,300 --> 00:07:59,740
when I was looking for you.

104
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:03,580
I was wondering

105
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:05,020
what was on your mind.

106
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:07,780
So, have you figured it out?

107
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:09,020
Of course not.

108
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:13,340
But I figured it out on my own terms.

109
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,580
What do you mean?

110
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,940
I had an exhausting life in the past.

111
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:26,580
I was too full of myself.

112
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,660
I was pretending

113
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:32,780
so that

114
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:34,500
I could feel better.

115
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:39,180
But after I got over the people
and the things that haunted me,

116
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:42,260
I finally got to move forward.

117
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:46,060
I'm glad that you figured it out.

118
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:51,180
What about you?

119
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:52,580
Have you figured it out?

120
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,100
What do I need to figure out?

121
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:07,780
About going back.

122
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,540
I will join you.

123
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,060
Let's go home together, okay?

124
