127
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:18,020
I won't hold back then.

128
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:20,700
What do you mean?

129
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:36,500
It's starting to get annoying.

130
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:45,540
So, do you two plan

131
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:47,260
to visit her father together?

132
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:53,860
Hurry up then.

133
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,100
