250
00:22:06,940 --> 00:22:08,020
You better return quickly, okay?

251
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:37,860
I'll make a move first.

252
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,140
Text me when you're there.

253
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,340
Do you think meeting your father now

254
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:45,860
