255
00:22:46,940 --> 00:22:47,460
Not at all.

256
00:22:52,020 --> 00:22:52,340
Okay then.

257
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:57,300
See you.

258
00:22:58,340 --> 00:22:58,780
